Bluesfest revealed the first version of its 2017 lineup on Tuesday with Tom Petty and the Heartbreakers headlining a big group that also includes Pink, Toby Keith and 50 Cent.
Ottawa Bluesfest's full 2017 lineup We asked music lovers to recommend some lesser-known bands performing at the annual festival in Ottawa, which runs this year from July 6-16.
